T1  - Savage's P3 Is Redundant
AU  - Hartmann, Lorenz
Y1  - 2020/01/01
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA17428
T2  - Econometrica
