T1  - Nonlinear Pricing in Village Economies
AU  - Attanasio, Orazio
AU  - Pastorino, Elena
Y1  - 2020/01/01
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA13918
T2  - Econometrica
